div.p: Identity map removed after higher-half transition: boot_page_directory[0] = 0; tlb_flush_all();

Sizing boot_page_directory: 4KB (4096B) identity_page_table: 4KB (1024 4B PTEs) kernel_page_table: 4KB (1024 4B PTEs) Total static PT: 12KB in .bss frame_bitmap (PMM): 128KB in .bss Covers: 4GB 4KB = 1M frames
